<div class="sh-hero">
  <div>
    <h1>Report Card <span class="sh-accent">Signing API</span></h1>
    <p>
      A secure API that streamlines digitally signing report cards for school administrators, replacing manual file
      handling on shared network drives with a fully automated, SharePoint-integrated workflow. Built with Python
      and FastAPI, it connects to the Microsoft Graph API and Azure Active Directory to authenticate users and
      access the correct SharePoint directories. The API automatically identifies the reporting term, applies the
      correct digital signature for each administrator, and generates signed copies in designated SharePoint
      folders. Access is governed by existing Active Directory security groups, and administrators are notified by
      email once their signed documents are ready.
    </p>
    <div class="sh-tech">
      <span>Python</span><span>FastAPI</span><span>Uvicorn</span><span>Microsoft Graph API</span>
      <span>Azure Active Directory</span><span>SharePoint</span><span>Microsoft SQL Server</span>
      <span>Microsoft Teams</span><span>ServiceNow</span>
    </div>
  </div>
